---
title: Pork Meatball 'Banh Mi' & Sriracha Mayo with Sweet Chilli Slaw & Fries
description: Inspired by the loveable Vietnamese sub, this version will take you to the streets of Hanoi on the first bite. Smear
over a sriracha mayo and pack in some sweet and soy pork meatballs to balance out a peppery sesame slaw. To add
something a bit different, serve with a side of fries to dip in some garlic aioli.

